<HL>
   France to Offer Plans
   To Ease Debt Burdens
   Of Certain Countries
   ----
   Special to The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
